			<h2 id="comments">Comment (1)
			</h2>
			<ol class="comments">
		
				<li id="comment-265">
					<article>
						<p>Company name is not very important for me, at least to some extent. I wouldn&#8217;t go work for a company named &#8220;Idiots&#8221; for example, but I don&#8217;t see any difference between &#8220;Zazbo&#8221; and &#8220;Google&#8221;.<br />
Same is for my name. Shit Face would not be a very comfortable name, I probably wouldn&#8217;t survive high school.</p>
